Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说夏川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了吗  死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她说了有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那暂时就只有我们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么
