Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你还真是个过分的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你这是做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}认真的吗  你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可爱的「女朋友」回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只是去办公室取个东西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说春咲同学不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了吗  死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哎呀  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为面前的不是偷腥猫  而是偷腥的吉娃娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁偷腥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是还趁着女朋友不在的时候赖在锐太同学身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是偷腥是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是这样  是社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我交到男朋友以前的练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  我之前不是也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想变成万人迷  就得先读完全套JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们社团得不到学生会认可  没有经费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就没法集齐全套JoJo了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来  春咲同学当然只能找别人的男朋友偷腥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们社团被风纪委员盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的风纪委员权力很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是乎这就是今天的课题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326.5,62)\frz1.3\fs22\t(0,600,\fs15.5)\1cA0868C\bord0}打倒风纪委员{\i1\fsp-10}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦  不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是要坐视社团被废止咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加社团人数怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加两个人就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好提议  春咲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你的头盖骨下竟然有大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以为有什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红豆面包的馅儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才吃的是咖喱面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  是哪个都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就来创作社团的主题歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\bord0\1c765F60}来创作演出自我的少女会的「主题歌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,52.5)\fs15\1c856A6F\bord0}来创作演出自我的少女会的「主题歌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看了歌曲的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能结束战争  让敌人改过自新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能打倒终极Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的能量传播能够超越语言  国界和种族的阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果是电视剧或者动画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可能因为听到某首歌而回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以歌曲会成为作品的门面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说如果借助主题歌来宣传我社团的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生们就会嚷着「请让我加入吧」蜂拥而至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  我想到了一首好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那春咲同学请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目是「和你的羁绊是汪汪喵」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE  LOVE  汪汪  汪汪喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐我说你  呐我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪了头发哦  有没注意到？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有三厘米  有没注意到？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那么和你的距离  就是三厘…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我全部听完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没想过要更多地表现人类的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现孤独灵魂的彷徨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这恋爱头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听这篇真正的诗歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后颤抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(429,323)\fs20}世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目是「腐坏至极的这个时代」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哇  等等等等  给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界  已然腐坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  就让我来制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是小孩就轻视我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(397,323)\fs20}Beast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街坊可是唤我为「暴走兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407.5,323)\fs20}Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我将一切归为虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}锐 认真听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我  我  我  我  Oh  零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  快点注意到我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管时光怎么流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你的羁绊都不会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事吗  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没有  没有  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴得再紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就看不出是男女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太同学  你有什么事瞒着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在社团活动室你也在偷瞄春咲同学的脸色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在我眼前对其他女生温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这独占欲是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不能告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就在全校同学面前朗读这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320.5,323)\fs20}Be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,323)\fs20}My
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(419,323)\fs20}Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守护我的四位美·舞·天使们」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能和别人讨论情书的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管后果怎样  这件事我不会说出口  绝不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对锐太同学来说  春咲同学很特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那边那位就是小凉的男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉没什么魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想看看小凉的男朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实你一点都不喜欢小凉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的  骗你的  开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人要你来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说是让我来看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然隔着电话  但是那边听上去很生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说送你回日本可不是为了让你为所欲为的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像通过这边议员之类的管道也了解了小凉在学校的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我会好好解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能做让小凉为难的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这家伙会这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小凉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我帮你好好解释的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠夺完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次见面之前把各种事情都考虑清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是私立根中女子学院初中部三年级的夏川真那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我真那哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉的…妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次做比接吻更棒的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不要问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你不是在颤抖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有不想被触及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也一样吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你不游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢被打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  难得上一回游泳课
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还挺喜欢游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘地浮在水面上  尽情玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像乔瑟夫和西撒那样用波纹气功在泳池水面上行走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺喜欢第1部和第2部的波纹战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副样子是想怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是故意遮遮掩掩摆架子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你不是说讨厌被打湿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这不是溺水了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉  真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快振作起来  真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗  真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我去把别的老师叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  山本  你在间接杀害你最喜欢的真凉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只能交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  全都这么露骨地盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前面  接吻什么的只是嘴和嘴贴在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群恋爱头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是高中生了  真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  溺水和初中高中没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天我对你的态度很奇怪  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我也是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌看到那孩子和锐太接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以为接吻什么的只是嘴和嘴贴在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却觉得非常讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是因为我打探了你的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和「男友」的初吻你明明还是用JoJo梗敷衍了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个接吻的事你就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也已经被覆盖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖  用什么覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…就是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反正接吻和人工呼吸没什么区别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫真那的女孩的吻对于我来说就是「那又怎样？」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总之别放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会忘得干干净净的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把老师叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo第2部的波纹战斗  我也很喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(142,77)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}主题：不得了了，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(174,130)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}怎么办，吉娃娃{\1c4838B9\i1\fsp-8}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,292)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}季堂同学和夏川真凉亲亲了{\1c4838B9\i1\fsp-8}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  虽然不算严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是周六  我却还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要的尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮我擦一下身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要温柔一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是说了让你温柔点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴啊  锐好久没来我的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  有多久没来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  锐  剩下的我自己来擦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个时候的筷子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  我擅自拿来了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种东西要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是我最宝贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那个回忆  在我心里永远不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是锐交了女朋友也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上了别的女生也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的羁绊就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封情书不是千和写的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们没有必要重新缔结羁绊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐  我也要人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  你不是有在呼吸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直陪着我吧  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去学人工呼吸也是为了千和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  千和  我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经彻底恢复了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  去上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  真凉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干吗一大早就秀恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是和青梅竹马在一起的时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁秀恩爱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你在啊  偷腥吉娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的就抢别人的男朋友  真是烦人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁偷腥了啊  你说谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}当然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这也是社团活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像看到了什么白色的纸片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你  我已经按捺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后  在天台等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,64)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,73)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0&}I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,128)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,139)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,192)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,204)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}U
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,256)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I  LOVE  U
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说是「遥远往昔的羁绊」有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是初次见面才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判断锐太并未取回前世的全部记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在尝试用这个世界的语言沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的咒文你读懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指「I  LOVE  U」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在希伯来语中的意思是「羁绊  苏醒吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这个世界被叫做秋筱姬香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的名字是Himeka·静·Heavensrain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,323)\fs20}Burning Prin Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前世的名字则是「晓之圣龙公主」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前世因强烈的羁绊与「晓之圣龙骑士」季堂锐太相互缔结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直好想见你  锐太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}啊  等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  秋筱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我希望你像以前一样叫我「公主」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：日文中「姫（Hime）」同时有「公主」之义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(418.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  公主  为什么你会知道「晓之圣龙骑士」的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在前世曾与你有过誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,323)\fs20}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要联手同邪龙族战斗直到生命的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(233.5,323)\fs20}Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和伟大黑暗进行最终决战的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问的不是设定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(418.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在哪里听说我是「晓之圣龙骑士」的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EKME点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EKME？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,323)\fs20}Ekimae
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个世界的语言来说就是「车站前」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是车站前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,323)\fs20}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572.5,323)\fs20}Saint War
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是锐太同被邪龙族操纵的现世界人之间展开的那次圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太释放的气场让封印得以解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于取回了前世的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是个现役「中二病」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐  那女孩是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个花花公子呢  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的可爱万人迷道具是…
